| `<file1>` | <what changed> |
| `<file2>` | <what changed> |

- **Approach:** <one sentence>
- **Risk level:** <Low|Medium|High>
- **Breaking change:** <Yes/No>

### Prevention

- **Mechanism:** <type guard / schema / assertion / lint rule / etc.>
